# Sprite Animation - Quy tac

## Khai niem
- **Frame** = 1 anh (`shime1.png`..`shime46.png`).
- **Clip** = chuoi frame + `defaultFrameMs` + `loop` (`PetFrameClip`).
- **Catalog** = `ShimejiFrameCatalog` (SSOT thu tu frame, KHONG hardcode noi khac).
- **Anchor** = `PetSpriteAnchor` (64,128) — toa do "chan pet" trong sprite 128x128.

## Cache bat buoc
KHONG goi `BitmapFactory.decodeStream` truc tiep trong Composable moi frame -> nhay/giật.
- Dung `PetSpriteCache.load(context, path)` (ConcurrentHashMap path -> ImageBitmap).
- Goi `PetSpritePrefetcher()` o top-level cua moi man (PetPlayField, PetOverlayContent) de prefetch 46 frame tren `Dispatchers.IO`.
- Khi doi path, GIU bitmap cu cho den khi load xong (KHONG vẽ Box xam placeholder).

## Kich thuoc hien thi
Sprite engine dung **pixel logical**. Vẽ Image phai khop:

```kotlin
// BAD: 128.dp -> 384px o may 3x, pet to gap 3 lan
modifier = Modifier.size(SPRITE_WIDTH_PX.dp)

// GOOD: dung 128 px logical
val w = with(density) { SPRITE_WIDTH_PX.toDp() }
modifier = Modifier.size(w)
```

## FPS / tick
- Tick engine = 16ms (~60 fps) cho ca Activity va Service.
- `PetFrameClip.defaultFrameMs` LA SO TICK SHIMEJI-EE (giong actions.xml goc), KHONG phai ms.
- `PetClipPlayback.SHIMEJI_TICK_MS = 20` -> ms thuc te = `defaultFrameMs * 20`.
  Vi du `Walk` defaultFrameMs=6 -> 120ms / frame ≈ 8 fps, du de mat thay tung buoc chan.
- KHONG sua thang gia tri trong `ShimejiFrameCatalog` cho dep mat; can chinh cam nhan toc do
  thi dieu chinh `SHIMEJI_TICK_MS` (giu nguyen catalog Shimeji goc).

## Huong nhin (lookRight)
Bo asset shime trong project huong TRAI (khac mot so ban goc). Khi `lookRight = true` (di sang phai)
can flip ngang de mat nhin dung huong di chuyen:
```kotlin
PetShimeSprite(path, flipHorizontal = snap.lookRight)
```
Implement bang `Modifier.graphicsLayer { scaleX = if (flip) -1f else 1f }` trong `PetShimeSprite`.

## Demo hanh dong (46 khung)
- Khong quet `shime1..46` tuan tu; dung `PetDemoActionPlaylist` (clip + thoi gian) de gom nhieu frame thanh hanh dong that.
- Nut `Het clip` van co the dung de duyet day du `ShimejiClipId` theo enum (ky thuat).

## Khi them clip moi
1. Khai bao `ShimejiClipId` moi.
2. Them entry trong `ShimejiFrameCatalog.clips`.
3. Engine chuyen sang clip do qua `s.copy(clipId = ...)`, KHONG hardcode path.
